  <brief_title>Local Tolerability and Safety of Povidone K25 Eye Drops (Artificial Tears Containing Povidone) Versus Placebo in Healthy Volunteers</brief_title>
  <official_title>Local Tolerability and Safety of Povidone K25 (Artificial Tears Containing Povidone) vs. Placebo in Healthy Volunteers</official_title>
  <sponsors>
