  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Healthy subjects

          -  Older than 18 years

          -  Ocular discomfort less than 20 mm on 100 mm visual analogue scale (VAS) prior to
             treatment

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Known hypersensitivity to any of the constituents of the medications

          -  Known allergic disposition (e.g. hay fever)

          -  Wearing of contact lenses

          -  Any kind of current eye disease (e.g. dry eye)

        Additional exclusion criteria are defined in the protocol
      </textblock>
